      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior paint retains a nice luster, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with all features and electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid, offering a smooth ride and reliable performance, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a dependable and well-cared-for vehicle.",
