    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty that looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept in pristine condition and treated with nothing but love. It drives like a total dream and is honestly as close to perfect as you can get. I'd love for it to go to a great home where it'll be just as pampered. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the zenith of the S54 platform, featuring its high-strung 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing. The mechanical synchronization is flawless, delivering linear power to the Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, including documented subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh with OEM bushings to maintain factory kinematics. The paint is deep and free of swirl marks, showcasing a mirror finish that reflects its sheltered life. This is a turn-key, collector-grade machine for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and zero deferred maintenance.",
